> **Theory Box: Evals Are Essential for Agents**
>
> Agents make multiple LLM calls per task — if each call has a 90% success rate, a 5-step agent has only 0.9^5 = 59% end-to-end reliability. Evals help you catch regressions, measure quality, and build confidence before deploying.

